ered.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 7}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?He stretches out the northern sky}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13  over empty space,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Suspending the earth upon nothing;\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 8}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?He wraps up the waters in his clouds,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 So that the clouds do not burst under their weight;\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 9}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?He shuts off the view of his throne,\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 Spreading out his cloud over it.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 10}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?He marks out the horizon}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13  on the surface of the waters;\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 He makes a boundary between light and darkness.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 11}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf13 \u160?The very pillars of heaven shake;\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1033\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1033\langnp1033\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\c